### Grid vs Flexbox – Quick Comparison

| Situation / Use Case                  | Best Tool       | Kyuu? (Asan Explanation) |
|---------------------------------------|-----------------|--------------------------|
| Simple horizontal/vertical alignment (navbar, buttons, centering) | **Flexbox**     | 1D mein bohot asaan aur intuitive |
| Navigation menu, card content alignment | **Flexbox**     | Items ko stretch, space-between, center karna easy |
| Full page / overall page layout       | **Grid**        | 2D control + better performance |
| Card grids, image galleries           | **Grid**        | `repeat(auto-fit, minmax())` se responsive magic |
| Layout jisme rows aur columns dono matter karte hain | **Grid**        | Ek jagah se dono directions control |
| Spanning items (ek item 2 columns cover kare) | **Grid**        | `grid-column: span 2;` bohot easy |
| Reducing media queries                | **Grid**        | `auto-fit` + `minmax()` se bohot kam breakpoints chahiye |
| Reordering items (visual order change) | **Flexbox** (`order`) | Thoda better aur simple |
| Complex overlapping or precise 2D positioning | **Grid**        | Grid lines aur areas se possible |

### Jab Grid se Flexbox Replace Kar Sakte Ho

1. **Card / Gallery Layouts** (Sabse Common)
```css
.cards {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 2rem;
}
```
(Flexbox mein yeh karna mushkil aur media queries zyada lagte hain)

2. **Navigation with Spanning Items**
```css
.nav-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr 1fr;
  gap: 1rem;
}
.ad { grid-column: span 3; }   /* Full width spanning */
```

3. **Holy Grail / Page Layout**
Grid se header, sidebar, main, footer ko ek baar mein perfectly define kar sakte ho (`grid-template-areas` ya lines se).

4. **Equal Height Columns + Responsive**
Grid automatically rows ko handle karta hai – Flexbox mein extra hacks lagte hain.

### Best Practice (Modern Approach)

- **Overall Page Structure** → **CSS Grid** use karo
- **Components ke andar** (buttons, nav items, card content) → **Flexbox** use karo
- Dono ko **nest** karo: Grid item ke andar Flexbox container banao

**Example Hybrid:**
```css
.page {                  /* Grid for structure */
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr;
}

.card {                  /* Flexbox for internal alignment */
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: space-between;
}
